WEBVTT

00:05:57.490 --> 00:06:01.030
What you probably did not know is that

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:05.070
staying healthy is also 
imperative for inner control.

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.256
It becomes easier to be stable.

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:15.280
Yet an even more important path is that

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:18.280
you let go of this belief that
uncertainty is your enemy.

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:24.320
Uncertainty makes life fun and spicy.

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:27.536
Whatever life throws at you,
keep playing accordingly.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:31.240
If you remember this always 
you will not make the mistake